{"about_the_game":"Welcome to the craziest chess-related experience you can find!<br><strong>Checkmate Kings</strong> is an <strong>action party game</strong> with <strong>twin stick shooters</strong>, <strong>bullet hells</strong> and <strong>2D fighters</strong> influences.<br>In this game, there is no health bar. If one chess piece hits you <strong>it's game over!</strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646910/extras/Choose_your_character.gif?t=1686844934\" /><br>Choose your character from a roster of 8 kings and queens inspired by fictional and historical characters.<br>You'll find each of them has a unique personality and playstyle!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646910/extras/Find_your_playstyle.gif?t=1686844934\" /><br>8 unique playstyles allow you to pressure your opponent however you like best!<br>Shoot, place pieces and dodge around to get the upper hand!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646910/extras/Steal_the_enemy_pieces.gif?t=1686844934\" /><br>Placing chess pieces, dodging, and pressuring your opponent is not all there is to the game! <br>Gather <strong>crowns</strong> and use their power to <strong>steal </strong>enemy pieces!<br>Turn the tides <strong>in a single move!</strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646910/extras/Customize_your_arena.gif?t=1686844934\" /><br>As you play you'll be able to unlock unique customization options for your arena!<br>Choose your favorite look and fill the stands with the best crowd you can find!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Online and local 1v1 multiplayer!<br></li><li>Arcade mode!<br></li><li>Progression system with unique customization possibilities!<br></li><li>8 characters with unique playstyles!<br>